{"tid":746932,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"為祖國點贊，上港更衣室出現謝謝字條🇨🇳","createTime":"2018-07-18T03:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T07:53:25.000Z","uid":20634,"like":13,"dislike":259,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"dfb570d1f0fb7aacb9fdce389acb0b0cfc9184f4","tid":746932,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:45:32.000Z","msg":"昨天晚上，上港客場1-1戰平魯能。賽後，上港全隊打掃了更衣室，球隊新聞官曬出了整理後的更衣室照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/114446_81ac5b4fcd52a85d346533e64f501a24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F114446_81ac5b4fcd52a85d346533e64f501a24.png&h=00f0d9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯世界杯淘汰賽上，日本隊被比利時絕殺淘汰，賽後他們在更衣室上留下了俄語的謝謝字條，引發網友熱評。世界杯過後，中超戰火重燃，本輪一場焦點大戰在魯能與上港之間展開，本場也是榜首之戰。上港新聞官在賽後發佈了兩張上港更衣室的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/114516_ec3562030bc60a85612e305890311148.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F114516_ec3562030bc60a85612e305890311148.png&h=9bc17fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上港最終客場1-1戰平魯能，雙方目前並列頭名。比賽結束後，上港全隊打掃了更衣室，從圖片中可以看出更衣室非常的整齊乾淨。<br />\n<br />\n而上港新聞官還發了一張特寫照片，是一張用英語寫的謝謝字條，上面還配上了中文：「感謝濟南奧體中心魯能大球場及貴俱樂部的熱情接待。歡迎貴俱樂部訪問上海體育場，與我們一起為球迷奉獻一場精彩的比賽。」"},{"pid":"ebe1e9cf8a2406e1d4247b1fe9c3950887e865e1","tid":746932,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346664f9874bc85683c17221ddb6a6db8fcd45cf","tid":746932,"uid":122750,"like":60,"dislike":2,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"who fuckin care支超?"},{"pid":"2f7658df5a1c015900e121832d57dccddc09b992","tid":746932,"uid":193642,"like":170,"dislike":0,"score":170,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/06/140203_bc47c42f42edda